<p class="nsw-docs__pattern-swatch-note">In a few 02 rows, the line colour uses White or 01 to keep pattern contrast at or above <code>3:1</code>.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Start with 01 and 02 from your main colour theme.</li>
  <li>If more colours are needed, add additional colour columns using 01 first, then 02.</li>
  <li>For a series of charts, keep category colours consistent across all charts so users can follow the story.</li>
</ul>

